---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roman Church — The Priesthood — Nazaryah"
  description="The Roman Empire did not abandon sun worship when it adopted Christianity. It absorbed Christianity into its existing solar religion. Mithraism, Sol Invictus, and the mystery tradition of Babylon flowed directly into what became the Roman Catholic Church."
>
  <div class="al-wrap">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="al-hero">
      <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/the-institutional-church" class="al-back">&#8592; Back to The Institutional Church</a>
      <p class="al-label">&#8213; The Priesthood · Full Study &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="al-title">Roman Church</h1>
      <p class="al-sub">
        From Mithras to Mass
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── ARTICLE BODY ── -->
    <article class="al-article">
      <div class="al-inner">

        <div class="al-prose">
          <p>
            The Roman Empire did not abandon sun worship when it adopted Christianity. It absorbed Christianity into its existing solar religion. Mithraism, the cult of Sol Invictus, and the mystery tradition of Babylon flowed directly into the structures, symbols, and calendar of what became the Roman Catholic Church.
          </p>
          <p>
            December 25th — the birthday of Sol Invictus — became the birthday of the Messiah. Sunday — the day of the sun — replaced the seventh-day Sabbath. The halo — the solar disc that had encircled the heads of Ra, Helios, Mithras, and Sol Invictus — was placed behind the heads of the apostles in church art. The obelisk — the ancient Egyptian monument to the sun god — stands in the center of St. Peter's Square to this day.
          </p>
          <p>
            This foundation is documented thoroughly on its own page. What matters here is that this was not a one-time event. It established a pattern — the pattern of an institution that calls itself the people of Yahuah while operating the machinery of Babylon. And that pattern is alive and thriving in the modern church.
          </p>
          <p>
            What makes the institutional church a branch of the same priesthood is not its architecture or its calendar — it is its claim of mediation. The Roman Catholic system teaches that you cannot access Yahuah directly. You need a priest, a sacrament, a building, a denomination. This is the exact structure of every pagan priesthood in history.
          </p>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="al-quote">
          <p class="al-quote-ref">1 Timothy 2:5</p>
          <p>"For there is one Elohim, and one mediator between Elohim and men, the man the Messiah Yahushua."</p>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="al-prose">
          <p>
            One mediator. Not a priesthood. Not a hierarchy. Not a denomination. Yahushua the Messiah — and Him alone. Any system that inserts itself between you and Yahuah is functioning as a pagan priesthood, regardless of what name it wears.
          </p>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="al-quote al-quote-closing">
          <p class="al-quote-ref">Revelation 18:4</p>
          <p>"Come out of her, my people, that ye be not partakers of her sins, and that ye receive not of her plagues."</p>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="al-seal">&#10022; &nbsp; &#10022; &nbsp; &#10022;</div>

      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- ── BACK BUTTON ── -->
    <section class="al-footer-nav">
      <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/the-institutional-church" class="al-back-btn">&#8592; Back to The Institutional Church</a>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .al-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0e0904 0%, #1a1208 20%, #160f07 100%);
    color: #f0e0bf;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .al-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #4a3218;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(180, 100, 20, 0.18), transparent 65%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0602 0%, #1a1208 100%);
  }

  .al-back {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #6a4820;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .al-back:hover { color: #c4a46b; }

  .al-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #8a6028;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .al-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .al-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
    color: #c4a46b;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .al-article { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  .al-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .al-prose {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #d9c9a8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .al-prose p { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .al-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .al-prose em { color: #c4a46b; font-style: italic; }
  .al-prose strong { color: #e8d5a8; font-weight: 600; }

  .al-h2 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 3.5rem 0 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #3a2510;
  }

  .al-quote {
    margin: 1.75rem 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #7a4a18;
    background: rgba(10, 6, 2, 0.4);
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
  }
  .al-quote p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #c4ad84;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .al-quote-ref {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px !important;
    font-style: normal !important;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #8a5a28 !important;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
  }

  .al-quote-closing {
    border-left-color: #c4a46b;
    background: rgba(186, 117, 23, 0.05);
  }

  .al-seal {
    text-align: center;
    color: #6a4820;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 8px;
    margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .al-footer-nav {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
  }

  .al-back-btn {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #6a4820;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .al-back-btn:hover { color: #c4a46b; }
</style>
